```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Farm Worker
    participant UI as React Component
    participant Dexie as IndexedDB (Dexie.js)
    participant Sync as Sync Engine
    participant Firestore as Firestore Cloud

    User->>UI: Enter egg count (50 eggs)
    UI->>Dexie: Save {date, quantity, createdAt}
    Note over Dexie: Instant - works offline
    UI-->>User: Saved confirmation

    Note over Sync: When connectivity available

    Sync->>Dexie: Read pending changes
    Dexie-->>Sync: unsynced records
    Sync->>Firestore: batchWrite(records)
    Firestore-->>Sync: Acknowledged
    Sync->>Dexie: Mark as synced
    UI-->>User: Sync indicator turns green
```
